    "description": "<p><u><strong>Who are WE?</strong></u></p>\n<p>we are AUX – the best team dedicated to planning and executing any event.</p>\n<p>The experience counts, doesn’t it?</p>\n<p>AUX connects brands and people. And in the business of standing out, we know how to bring brands to life with meaningful engagement, creative immersions and exciting touchpoints.</p>\n<p>We are problem solvers and we get in the trenches because we love what we do. Our ideas are bold, our executions are strong and we challenge the impossible.</p>\n<p>Since 2001, we have been trusted by some of the biggest and most exciting brands. From large-scale colourful festivals and extravaganzas to intimate activations and events, our work aims to create fans and advocates for our clients.</p>",
